258
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:44,630
Like a fool...

259
00:25:44,630 --> 00:25:49,250
But since that day, not even a day
went by where I didn't feel guilty, Joon Woo.

260
00:25:49,250 --> 00:25:52,380
I'm really sorry and... really...

261
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:58,220
I don't know why I did that.

262
00:25:58,220 --> 00:26:03,520
I regret it a lot.
I'm sorry, Joon Woo.

263
00:26:09,470 --> 00:26:12,590
To be honest, I resented you guys a lot

264
00:26:13,570 --> 00:26:16,550
because I had a really hard time.

265
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:26,890
I'll accept your apology for what you did wrong.

266
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:38,990
You know we're starting the mentor-mentee program, right?

267
00:26:38,990 --> 00:26:43,830
