00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:15,240
If you don't do any of the homework I give you,
I'm quitting on the spot.

272
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:19,400
Okay. No, no.
Yes, Ma'am.

273
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,810
Work hard.

274
00:27:22,670 --> 00:27:27,600
Right. If you manage to be in the top 200 in the class,
I'll watch a movie with you.

275
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:34,430
Uh, uh, Ro Mi.
What if I'm in the top 100?

276
00:27:34,430 --> 00:27:38,500
One hundred?
Don't worry. That will never happen.

277
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:44,370
I mean, but still,
if even in your imagination I'm in the top 100?

278
00:27:47,710 --> 00:27:50,460
I could date you.

279
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:55,330
- Hey, what happened?!
