280
00:27:55,330 --> 00:28:01,220
This... is low in calories.
It's vegetables in whole grain bread.

281
00:28:02,690 --> 00:28:05,470
He's the one who broke up with me.

282
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:09,410
He made me some sandwiches.
Is he carrying fire in one hand and water in the other?

283
00:28:09,410 --> 00:28:14,470
- Da Huin.
- That's it for today.

284
00:28:20,330 --> 00:28:22,440
Yoon So Ye.

285
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:24,960
- By the way...
- Hi.

286
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:30,150
Can I ask you something?
