00:28:57,970 --> 00:29:02,730
Do some self-reflecting, Lee Gi Tae.
Watch whom you hang out with.

295
00:29:02,730 --> 00:29:05,950
Hey! Who are you to say that to him?

296
00:29:05,950 --> 00:29:11,040
He'll repent for whatever he did wrong!
Worry about yourself!

297
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:16,980
Cool!

