00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:27,120
Then you're not lacking either.

299
00:29:29,950 --> 00:29:34,460
Someone who's not lacking at all says she likes you.

300
00:29:37,820 --> 00:29:43,050
You're kind of good at drawing.
The ladybug is cute.

