00:33:06,340 --> 00:33:09,310
Teacher, tell me something honestly.

326
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:15,500
If you don't speak honestly, I'm not letting you leave.

327
00:33:15,500 --> 00:33:18,510
There's a problem, isn't there?

328
00:33:19,870 --> 00:33:22,640
The OMR card.
(Optical Mark Reader scans an answer card)

329
00:33:23,620 --> 00:33:26,600
It was rigged. There are exactly two questions.

