00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:29,040
Hui Yeong's admission is a huge deal.

331
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:32,800
I learned about it by accident.
He made a mistake.

332
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:36,210
I also shouldn't have done that.
I really knew that,

333
00:33:36,210 --> 00:33:38,990
but my family situation was very difficult then.

334
00:33:38,990 --> 00:33:42,230
I made a deal with Hui Yeong's father.

335
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:47,150
No.
No matter how needy you were, how could you?

336
00:33:47,150 --> 00:33:53,280
That's why I went into hiding.
I can't sleep well. I can't eat.

337
00:33:54,470 --> 00:33:57,210
The vice-principal.
Does he know?

338
00:33:57,210 --> 00:34:00,980
No one knows.
I am the only one. Hui Yeong doesn't know.

339
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:05,970
Hui Yeong probably thinks he got it right
thanks to marking the card wrong, too.

340
00:34:07,260 --> 00:34:10,780
There's no other alternative.
Please step forward and explain it.

341
00:34:10,780 --> 00:34:13,100
Then Hui Yeong's family and I will both die.

342
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:15,330
If you do this, then something bad
will happen to Hui Yeong instead!

343
00:34:15,330 --> 00:34:20,210
You need to speak up about what happened!
He's a kid with a bright future!

344
00:34:22,130 --> 00:34:23,500
Please set it right.

345
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:29,470
Something done among the adults,
the adults should reveal it and pay for their wrongdoing.

346
00:34:30,060 --> 00:34:34,520
Then give me a little time.

347
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:42,200
My Ji Min

348
00:34:42,200 --> 00:34:46,090
Yes, Ji Min. Hello?

349
00:34:47,720 --> 00:34:50,980
Teacher, I have something to tell you.

350
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:55,610
Are you okay?
Are you sick? Is something wrong?

351
00:34:55,610 --> 00:35:00,080
I... need some time.

352
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:05,200
- What, what kind of time?
- Whether I can continue to date you...

353
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:08,900
If I'm worthy of it, I'm not sure...

354
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:12,650
What do you mean... worthy?

355
00:35:12,650 --> 00:35:16,720
I think I'm lacking in many ways.

356
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:22,070
- I'm sorry.
- Ji Min, Ji Min. Hel—

357
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:44,040
Your drawings aren't bad.
First, what you have to prepare depends on your grades.

358
00:35:44,040 --> 00:35:48,580
With your grades, I think preparing something
in the basic design category would be good.

359
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:53,890
For the schools that look at basic design categories, your skills test grade account for 60-100% even of your total grade.

360
00:35:53,890 --> 00:36:00,980
So if you take good care of your grades and prepare for
your skills test, you have a lot of schools you could go to.

361
00:36:03,080 --> 00:36:10,380
By chance,
would it be okay if there's a blemish on my records?

362
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:13,730
Like a forced transfer...

363
00:36:13,730 --> 00:36:18,780
It could affect it, but each school
has their own grading system.

364
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:22,910
If you're looking at the higher-level schools,
your grades would have to be better,

365
00:36:22,910 --> 00:36:30,070
but if not, you could look into schools
that only look at your skill, so that's a possibility.

366
00:36:30,070 --> 00:36:34,650
Oh, I see.
Then about what about tuition?

367
00:36:34,650 --> 00:36:41,410
Well, do you want me to give you
an idea of academy costs?

368
00:36:42,130 --> 00:36:44,650
Yes.

369
00:38:15,240 --> 00:38:19,800
- Give it to me, I'll do it.
- Just study over there instead of using up your energy.

370
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:23,760
It's good for concentrating anyway.

371
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:26,690
It's because of Noona Ji Min, right?

372
00:38:29,750 --> 00:38:31,660
Do you know too?

373
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:37,890
She talked about you.
That you're so nice but that she doesn't feel ready yet.

374
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:43,990
Wha... what? Ready for what?
Is she going fishing? Hiking?

375
00:38:45,330 --> 00:38:48,000
Just try waiting, even though it must be hard.

376
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:54,020
Like you and Soo Bin?
Even though it must be hard?

377
00:38:58,070 --> 00:39:03,690
Seriously, liking someone is difficult. Right?

378
00:39:03,690 --> 00:39:09,480
Whether you're 18, 28, or 38.

379
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:14,590
Teach... you're 28?

380
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:20,880
Whether you're 48 or 58...

381
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:25,280
or 68 or 78...

382
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:32,570
88... or 98... 108.

383
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:37,040
Hey, Joon Woo.
Eat a lot. Here.

384
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:39,750
Hey, I have some expectations for your exams.

385
00:39:39,750 --> 00:39:43,720
You seem to be studying hard.
Sense of coming up on your grades?

386
00:39:44,740 --> 00:39:48,350
You've decided to put your all into it?

387
00:39:54,720 --> 00:40:00,470
If I get good grades this time,
I thought Soo Bin's mom might get a better impression of me.

388
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:06,310
So I'm studying hard... but I still am thinking this:

389
00:40:06,310 --> 00:40:12,060
even if my grades come up,
even if I come in the top of the class,

390
00:40:14,350 --> 00:40:17,690
would her mother care at all?

391
00:40:18,910 --> 00:40:22,230
What good is all this?

392
00:40:23,290 --> 00:40:30,890
The effort I'm putting in right now, is it my best?
Those types of thoughts.

393
00:40:30,890 --> 00:40:37,020
Oh, don't lose heart.
Who cares if Soo Bin's mom doesn't think as highly of you?

394
00:40:37,020 --> 00:40:42,500
It's for yourself only, how you look to yourself,
that you're doing this well.

395
00:40:42,500 --> 00:40:47,470
You're doing this much,
you're making your best effort in life.

396
00:40:48,790 --> 00:40:51,660
Then after that?

397
00:40:51,660 --> 00:40:58,250
Then, after that...
then I suppose the next story will unfold itself?

398
00:40:58,250 --> 00:41:02,930
Hey, Joon Woo, think about when you first transferred.

399
00:41:02,930 --> 00:41:06,510
You didn't run away then, so you met Soo Bin,

400
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:10,590
and you also met the world's best teacher like me.

401
00:41:10,590 --> 00:41:13,680
You have to answer.

402
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,710
Yes.

403
00:41:15,710 --> 00:41:21,400
Joon Woo, don't worry about the future and just do it.

404
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:25,960
Now.
Without regret. Huh?

405
00:41:30,050 --> 00:41:31,880
Yes.

406
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:36,500
Seriously, if you were an adult,
we'd be having some soju. But for now,

407
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:40,090
let's have some water at least.

408
00:41:40,090 --> 00:41:43,920
- One shot!
- With the water?

