444
00:45:58,300 --> 00:46:01,510
- Again?
- I have to hurry to open the shop.

445
00:46:01,510 --> 00:46:02,860
But Auntie is there.

446
00:46:02,860 --> 00:46:07,210
Well, she doesn't feel well these days.

447
00:46:07,210 --> 00:46:10,940
You don't seem okay either.
