451
00:46:22,820 --> 00:46:27,840
Then first, fish that's good for your brain.

452
00:46:32,290 --> 00:46:34,600
You're doing well with Soo Bin, right?

453
00:46:34,600 --> 00:46:37,640
I wonder if her mom's busy.
