454
00:46:37,640 --> 00:46:40,000
We were going to be like sisters.

455
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:43,670
She doesn't know yet about you two dating, right?

456
00:46:46,190 --> 00:46:49,870
Once the exams are over, tell her.

457
00:46:49,870 --> 00:46:53,850
She might seem a little,

458
00:46:53,850 --> 00:46:58,140
a tiny bit rough, but she's a very cool person
once you get to know her.

459
00:46:58,140 --> 00:47:03,890
She seems so different from me,
but we get along completely.

460
00:47:03,890 --> 00:47:05,650
Oh, I might miss the bus!

461
00:47:05,650 --> 00:47:11,560
Oh, Joon Woo, do well on the exams.
I'll send you good wishes while working.

462
00:47:11,560 --> 00:47:13,320
Thank you.

